  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Acute ischemic stroke

          -  Occlusion demonstrated by transcranial Doppler ultrasound

          -  Eligible for tPA

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Right to left cardiac shunt

          -  Moderate to severe COPD

          -  Uncontrolled hypertension
      </textblock>
